title: 820-3437-B Charges on 85w but will not charge on 60w nor 45w
message:
I've had 2 A1466 boards with this same issue.
820-3437-B Charges on 85w but will not charge on 60w nor 45w after liquid damage. 
Any tips would be much appreciated.

title: 820-3437-B Charges on 85w but will not charge on 60w nor 45w
message: Run ASD EFI (ASD 3S156), lets see if any error pops up, where was water damage???

title: 820-3437-B Charges on 85w but will not charge on 60w nor 45w
message: I'd say bad IO board or flat cable.

title: 820-3437-B Charges on 85w but will not charge on 60w nor 45w
message:
We've tried both I/O Board & Flat Cable. 
Didn't think about running ASD but will try that.

title: 820-3437-B Charges on 85w but will not charge on 60w nor 45w
message: Did you check the sense resistors around ISL6259?
